## Parte 2 — Clear Configs and reload equipment (Rt e Sw)

### Router (RT1-St)
```
enable
erase startup-config
reload
```

### Switch (SW1-St)
```
enable
erase startup-config
delete flash:vlan.dat
reload
```

### Ajustar SDM Template (se necessário)
```
enable
show sdm prefer

configure terminal
sdm prefer dual-ipv4-and-ipv6 default
end
copy running-config startup-config
reload
```

