## Parte 12 — Multi-Location Wireless Deployment (AP1-St)

### Reset e configuração inicial do AP1-St (consola)
```
Username: Cisco
Password: Cisco
> enable
Password: Cisco
# capwap ap ip address 172.20.13.226 255.255.255.248
# capwap ap ip default-gateway 172.20.13.225
# capwap ap controller ip address 172.20.7.6
```

### Passos na GUI da WLC (depois do AP1-St aparecer associado)
- Confirmar que o AP1-St entra no AP Group **Split-APs**.
- Associar as WLANs **WIRELESS-St** e **GUESTS-St** ao AP Group Split-APs (WLANs > Advanced > AP Groups > WLANs).
- Selecionar o AP1-St: General > AP Mode = FlexConnect.
- Advanced > associar ao AP Group correto (Split-APs).
- High Availability > confirmar nome/endereço da WLC1-Zg.
- Após reboot do AP: FlexConnect > VLAN Support > Native VLAN = 5. Aplicar.
- VLAN Mapping: WIRELESS-St → VLAN 50, GUESTS-St → VLAN 60.

